{
  "texts": [
    "The proposed metrics demonstrate both within-category and betweencategory associations, with the potential for negative or positive correlations among them.",
    "Within-category relations refer to the associations among metrics within the same category.",
    "For instance, within the accuracy metrics category, up-to-dateness and groundedness show a positive correlation, as ensuring the chatbot utilizes the most recent and valid information enhances the factual accuracy of answers, thereby increasing groundedness.",
    "Between-category relations occur when metrics from different categories exhibit correlations.",
    "For instance, metrics in trustworthiness and empathy may be correlated."
  ]
}